  "body": "### Description\n\nIn RHTAP and more generally with devfile.io, they use staged dockerfiles which is important for CI builds.\r\nhttps://github.com/devfile-samples/devfile-sample-code-with-quarkus/blob/main/src/main/docker/Dockerfile.jvm.staged\r\nhttps://github.com/devfile-samples/devfile-sample-code-with-quarkus/blob/main/src/main/docker/Dockerfile.jvm.staged.dockerignore\r\n\r\nAs you can see they are maintaining their own Dockerfile for this meaning it could break at any moment.\r\n\r\nAlso maybe there is way to avoid the dockerignore.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
